Using the :zephyr:ref:`LED driver API <led_api>` with given LED strip.
That is:

| :hwftlbl-led:`RGB` : :dts:`aliases { led-strip = &led_strip; };`
| :hwftlbl-led:`WS2812` : :dts:`led_strip: &ws2812_1x1 {};`

